		{ ref: `Romans 8:1`, slug: `romans`, ch: 8, text: `There is therefore now no condemnation for those who are in Christ Jesus.`, note: `If guilt has been the background hum of your faith, hear this: in Christ, the verdict over you is already love, not condemnation.` },
