	offersIntroHtml={`So much of devotion can feel like proving yourself to God. Here is what your Father offers you instead — freely, because by grace you are already His.`}
	offersBlocks={[
		{ heading: `A Father who runs to meet you`, bodyHtml: `You do not have to crawl home and earn your way back. <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/luke/15" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">While you are still far off, the Father runs to you</a> — filled with compassion, arms already open.` },
		{ heading: `Adoption instead of fear`, bodyHtml: `Faith was never meant to be lived as anxious slavery. <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/romans/8" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">You received the Spirit of adoption</a>, who teaches your heart to cry "Abba, Father" — the closest, most tender name for God.` },
		{ heading: `Assurance of love, lavished not measured`, bodyHtml: `You don't have to wonder where you stand. <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/1-john/3" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">See the great love the Father has lavished on you</a> — that you should be called His child, and that is what you are.` },
		{ heading: `Grace you can finally rest in`, bodyHtml: `The striving to earn and keep His favor can stop. <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/ephesians/2" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">You are saved by grace, through faith</a> — the gift of God, not the wage of your works. You are already fully accepted.` },
	]}
