	whyBlocks={[
		{ heading: `Meet the Father the gospel already proclaims`, bodyHtml: `Your faith centers on "Our Father" — yet God can still feel distant. The Father's Heart Bible™ reveals God as a <em>Father</em> wherever Scripture reveals Him as Father — from <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/genesis/1" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Genesis 1</a> onward — so the nearness you long for meets you on the page, the same Word the Church has treasured for two thousand years.` },
		{ heading: `Free to read and hear Scripture for yourself`, bodyHtml: `No account, no purchase, no app. <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Read it free online</a> with audio on every chapter — listen on your commute, in a quiet hour, or before Mass. The Church has always invited the faithful to encounter God in His Word; here it is, in plain English, ready when you are.` },
		{ heading: `It speaks to the longing for assurance`, bodyHtml: `If you carry quiet guilt or wonder whether you have done enough, you are not alone — and Scripture speaks directly to it. Begin with our <a href="/verses/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">verses by topic</a> on grace and the love of God, or learn to speak to Him simply with our <a href="/guides/how-to-pray/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">how-to-pray guide</a> — moving from recited words toward a real conversation with your Father.` },
